arts.ttl: Ex AC Milan Star To Return To Starting XI For Inter Milan Vs Udinese – Only One Doubt For Chivu
arts.sum: Hakan Calhanoglu will start for Inter Milan in tomorrow’s Serie A clash with Udinese. This according to today’s print edition of Rome-based newspaper Corriere dello Sport, via FCInterNews. They report that the only selection doubt is between Petar Sucic and Henrikh Mkhitaryan. Inter Milan take on Udinese in Serie A tomorrow evening.
